data.description: This charming well maintained former model 3-2-2 split bedroom home with an open floor plan, is perfect for entertaining and raising a family. The skylight in the large eat in kitchen, provides an abundance of natural lighting during the day. Recent updates include new seamless gutters along back and sides of home, and new tile landing at back entrance.
